Hello and welcome to the @MrCodeInc Blog! I blog about **code and stuff.**

# My New cool project.

So I made this website that can help **YOU** learn how to code. **YOU** can view it [Here](https://mrcodeinc.github.io/CodeLoad/) sooooooo yeah. It's a thing. **K Bye**

# I made something...

Sooooooooooo I made a thing and if you want to see it's [here](https://mrcodeinc.github.io/supercoolwebsite/)

# What do I make?

Sooooooo I want to make something cool with some code but I don't know what to make. That's where **YOU** come in.
I want **YOU** to leave a comment on github telling me what to code. Thank **YOU** for reading this. **K Bye.**

# Hello World?

This my first post so I will tell you that you can help me make an amazing site by sending me edits to source code. that you see fit for this site. To get to the source code you can click button above that says view on github or you can click @MrCodeInc to go my github account page and look for it there. **K Bye.**
